divs: sighting detailson the evening of 5\21\09, i noticed that the sky looked cool and the reflection on the pond behind my house looked picturesque. so i took three photos of the landscape and noticed nothing unusual at the time. a few weeks later, i uploaded the photos to my computer and on the first photo i noticed a moving flash in the center of the sky. the next photo showed the shining object slip behind a tree to the left. i found these anomalous pictures to be quite interesting. i posted these photos on my facebook page and later noticed the the third photo shows the object speeding away on the upper right. this is very strange and i have no idea about what it was. i often take pictures of the seasonal changes behind my house. usually i will shoot two or three photos. what is strange here is that i believe that i took three pictures but there are three missing pictures?! images 262, 263 and 264 never showed up when i uploaded the files and i do not remember taking them. i am dumbfounded by this experience. something quite strange was out there that night and it wasn't a cessna, a helicopter or venus. et between recovered images: 1. img260 7:43:35 2. img261 7:43:38 3. img265 7:44:23 higher res pix available upon request.
Summary: I took three pictures of beautiful wetland behind my house, and a strange object appeared when I uploaded the images...
